Owncloud-Ajaxplorer

EXTRA INFO

Add 

"AUTH_DRIVER" = array(
		"NAME"          => "remote",
		"OPTIONS"       => array(
			"SLAVE_MODE"  => true,
			"USERS_FILEPATH" => "AJXP_INSTALL_PATH/data/plugins/auth.serial/users.ser",
			"LOGIN_URL" => "/",  // The URL to redirect to if a non-logged user tries to access AjaXplorer, optional
			"LOGOUT_URL" => "/",  // The URL to redirect upon login out, optional
			"SECRET" => "myprivatesecret",// the secret key that you will pass to the glueCode when communicating with it (see below)
			"TRANSMIT_CLEAR_PASS"   => false ) // Don't touch this. It's unsafe (and useless here) to transmit clear password.
	)

to your ajaxplorer/conf/bootstrap_plugins.php


	
